$$
\text{三角函数常用的}
\\
\text{恒等式} \sin ^2\alpha +\cos ^2\alpha =1   
\\
\sec ^2\alpha =\tan ^2\alpha +1   \cot ^2\alpha +1=\csc ^2\alpha 
\\

\\
\cot \alpha =\frac{1}{\tan \alpha}
\\
\sec \alpha =\frac{1}{\cos \alpha}\,\,    \csc \alpha =\frac{1}{\sin \alpha}
\\
$$


$$
\\
\text{倍角公式}
\\

\\
\sin 2\alpha =2\sin \alpha \cos \alpha 
\\
\cos 2\alpha =\cos ^2\alpha -\sin ^2\alpha =2\cos ^2\alpha -1=1-2\sin ^2\alpha 
\\
\tan 2\alpha =\frac{2\tan \alpha}{1-\tan ^2\alpha}
\\
$$


$$
\\
\text{半角公式，}\sin a\text{和}\cos a\text{的从}\cos\text{的二倍角公式可以推导出来}
\\

\\
\cos 2\alpha =2\cos ^2\alpha -1
\\
\cos 2\alpha +1=2\cos ^2\alpha 
\\
\frac{\cos 2\alpha +1}{2}=\cos ^2\alpha 
\\
\text{于是有}\cos ^2\alpha =\frac{\cos 2\alpha +1}{2}
\\
$$
$$
\\
\cos ^2\frac{\alpha}{2}=\frac{1+\cos \alpha}{2}
\\
\sin ^2\frac{\alpha}{2}=\frac{1-\cos \alpha}{2}
\\
\tan \frac{\alpha}{2}=\frac{\sin \alpha}{1+\cos \alpha}
\\
$$
$$
\\
